title: F-Zero GX Dr Stuard (Jeff & Toad Air Team Challengers) OC ReMix
info:
Remix of Dr. Stewart's theme from the game F-Zero GX for GameCube. Original song composed by Daiki Kasho.

I don't think it's demoscene-related, though it's an awesome song. :)


SORRY, AWESOME SONG DOES NOT MAKE IT FIT NECTARINE. Rejected.
